  "description": {
   "en": "1-2: Spotlight Lover  \nAlthough Nioujima's mother forced him to join a talent audition, he is actually a plain and boring shut-in. What happens when the new Assistant Director Kouyagi sees through his disguise?  \n  \n3: Night Magic Hour  \nAn AD-in-training and a seemingly cold senpai. He doesn't know what his senpai feels for him and he is fretting about it. But it may be that he himself has never said anything.  \n  \n4-5: Cinematic Mirror  \nSecond generation Shimon is troubled by his father's shadow. One night, a young fortune-teller gives him some advice."
